侵蝕一國兩制的重要原則」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥續稱，維護《基本法》賦予的權利和自由、維護香港法治（即是司法獨立、公平審訊、尋求法律公義的權利）同樣重要。另一重要原則，是她稱之為「香港制度優勢」，即由法庭系統到執法系統，包括警隊。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">提到警隊時，她進一步稱「不幸地，他們被誤解，最近亦受到很多攻擊。」</span></span></strong><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n而前宗主國英國首相 Boris Johnson則未有出席達沃斯經濟論壇，他接受英國傳媒訪問時表示<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>要對國民做實事，不是和富豪喝香檳</strong></span></span> (Our focus is on delivering for the people, not champagne with billionaires)， 更形容<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">論壇是「明星秀」，只是一群自大狂圍爐取暖，互相吹捧</span></strong></span>(a great big constellation of egos involved in massive mutual orgies of adulation)."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:52:08.000Z","msg":"Fucking chief of special administration Hong Kong, you must go to hell"},{"pid":"5255e7ce16e739e85e358ac86b8a35fa9f18e5fd","tid":1838451,"uid":101110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:55:04.000Z","msg":"雜種: 叫條八婆講少兩句當幫忙"},{"pid":"0d572d869a02b53249b8208b97456bfd74cc0c7c","tid":1838451,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b799be94403d8b5b5d637b63ef36c0141297445","tid":1838451,"uid":209390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:45:46.000Z","msg":"777度左咁耐D稿..老閪都要講埋先走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好打得"},{"pid":"a45f8765c6418f57b48f1a34bea551b9ee6e9bbd","tid":1838451,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f4a754a99b4e374084c4b71227e348e12bef62e","tid":1838451,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cited